<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" ng-app="canvas">
<head>
  %= include 'header.inc', title => 'KororaProject'
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-container">

    %= include 'navigation.inc', active => 'support'

    <div class="page-content">
      <!-- CONTENT -->

      <div id="page-about" class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <ol class="breadcrumb">
              <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
              <li class="active">Support</li>
            </ol>
            <h1 class="page-title"><strong>Support.</strong> You have a question?</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <p>We do hope that you won't run into any problems with Korora, however no system is perfect!</p>

            <h2>Engage the Community</h2>
            <p><a href="/support/engage">Engage</a> is your portal to interact with the primary developers and wider community. It allows you to submit your problems, ask questions, suggest an idea and even just say thanks.</p>

            <h2>Internet Relay Chat (IRC)</h2>
            <p>The core development team plus a few lurkers can usually be found on our IRC channel, #korora on the chat.freenode.net servers.</p>

            <h2>Social</h2>
            <p>We are also ready and waiting on <a href="https://plus.google.com/+KororaProjectOrg">Google+</a></li>, <a href="http://facebook.com/kororaproject">Facebook</a></li>, <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/kororaproject">Twitter</a> and <a href="http://identi.ca/kororaproject">Identi.ca</a></p>
            <div class="callout callout-info">
              <p>If you're after assistance specifically for Fedora, perhaps try the <a href="https://fedoraforum.org">community forums</a>, <a href="https://admin.fedoraproject.org/mailman/listinfo/users">official user mailing list</a>, or the #fedora IRC channel on chat.freenode.net.</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- END CONTENT -->
    </div>
  </div>

  %= include 'footer.inc'

  <!-- MODALS -->
  %= include 'authenticate.inc'

  <!-- SCRIPTS -->
  %= include 'scripts.inc'

</body>
</html>
